criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy,

          -  Ambulatory,

          -  Recreationally active,

          -  Community dwelling

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Evidence of coronary heart disease;

          -  Congestive heart disease;

          -  Uncontrolled hypertension;

          -  Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease;

          -  Diabetes mellitus;

          -  Renal failure;

          -  Major orthopedic disability; and

          -  Smoking
